name: url
description: Provides a clickable link to a web link

propSpec.name: height
propSpec.desc: A string that defines the url's height (usually in px)

propSpec.name: width
propSpec.desc: A string that defines the url's width (usually in px)

propSpec.name: enableScroll
propSpec.desc: A string defining how scrolling should take place

propSpec.name: title
propSpec.desc: A string defining the title of the iframe
